description: Great valued combo features 4 piece black camera lens pouch set for small, medium, large and extra large lens. Each pouch is made of strong, stretchy and water resistant neoprene fabric and has a string and toggle closure with a plastic hook for those quick on the go moments when you need your lens now! This set makes a great starter set for someone who wants to protect their lens at an affordable price. Pouch Measurements: Thickness: 3mm, Small: 8" x 3.9", Medium: 10" x 5.5", Large: 10" x 7.0" and Extra Large: 10" x 8.6" (Diameter Opening x Depth of Bag).
